Detailed Description

SOCKET Network implementation based of socket (TCP). The initialization of such SOCKET Network is based on information in the properties files and into the extra properties passed as extra arguments. The properties files may have following informations for SOCKNET network: socknet.fileurl= <filename>; // file where to write IO to connect to this node socknet.bindurl = <url/string>; // the url on which to accept incomming connexion socknet.cachesize= <integer>; // maximal number of active connexions socknet.verboseon= <true/false>; // true iff verbose mode is activated
